org.dgfoundation.amp.ar.viewfetcher

Class DgEditorPropertyDescription

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dgfoundation.amp.ar.viewfetcher.DgEditorPropertyDescription
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PropertyDescription

    public class DgEditorPropertyDescription
extends java.lang.Object
implements PropertyDescription
    IMMUTABLEclass holding the data necessary reading the i18n value of a property translated through DG_EDITOR entries
    NEVER EVER MAKE THIS CLASS MUTABLE OR CONTAIN MUTABLE FIELDS
    The class fetches its data from a view which has rows of the form (activity_id, text, locale)
